<div class="pm-success-wrap">
  <div id="pm-success" class="pm-message pm-message--success pm-message--hidden">
    Herzlich willkommen! Deine Anmeldung ist eingegangen. Du erhältst in Kürze eine Bestätigungs-E-Mail.
  </div>
</div>

<div id="pm-wizard-overlay" class="pm-wizard-overlay" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="Anmeldung Passivmitgliedschaft">
  <div id="pm-wizard-modal" class="pm-wizard__modal">

    <div class="pm-wizard__header">
      <h2 class="pm-wizard__title">Passivmitglied werden</h2>
      <button id="pm-wizard-close" class="pm-wizard__close" aria-label="Schliessen">&times;</button>
    </div>

    <div class="pm-progress" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="pm-progress__dot pm-progress__dot--active" data-step="1"></span>
      <span class="pm-progress__dot" data-step="2"></span>
      <span class="pm-progress__dot" data-step="3"></span>
      <span class="pm-progress__dot" data-step="4"></span>
      <span class="pm-progress__dot" data-step="5"></span>
      <span class="pm-progress__dot" data-step="6"></span>
      <span class="pm-progress__label" id="pm-step-label">Schritt 1 von 6</span>
    </div>

    <div class="pm-wizard__body">

      <div class="pm-step pm-step--active" data-step="1">
        <h3>Dein Feld</h3>
        <p>Du hast folgendes Feld gewählt:</p>
        <div class="pm-field-preview" id="pm-step1-field">Feld Nr. –</div>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#666;">Klicke «Weiter» um fortzufahren, oder schliesse den Dialog um ein anderes Feld zu wählen.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pm-step" data-step="2">
        <h3>Mitgliedsstufe wählen</h3>
        <div class="pm-wizard-levels">
          <label class="pm-wizard-level pm-wizard-level--bronze">
            <input type="radio" name="levelKey" value="Bronze" />
            <span class="pm-wizard-level__badge">Bronze</span>
            <span class="pm-wizard-level__info">
              <span class="pm-wizard-level__name">Hallenbodenbesitzer</span>
              <span class="pm-wizard-level__fee">CHF 50.–/Jahr</span>
            </span>
          </label>
          <label class="pm-wizard-level pm-wizard-level--silber">
            <input type="radio" name="levelKey" value="Silber" />
            <span class="pm-wizard-level__badge">Silber</span>
            <span class="pm-wizard-level__info">
              <span class="pm-wizard-level__name">Chnebler</span>
              <span class="pm-wizard-level__fee">CHF 100.–/Jahr</span>
            </span>
          </label>
          <label class="pm-wizard-level pm-wizard-level--gold">
            <input type="radio" name="levelKey" value="Gold" />
            <span class="pm-wizard-level__badge">Gold</span>
            <span class="pm-wizard-level__info">
              <span class="pm-wizard-level__name">Cüpli-Chnebler</span>
              <span class="pm-wizard-level__fee">CHF 200.–/Jahr</span>
            </span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pm-step" data-step="3">
        <h3>Deine Angaben</h3>
        <div class="pm-form-group">
          <label for="pm-firstName">Vorname <span class="pm-required">*</span></label>
          <input type="text" id="pm-firstName" autocomplete="given-name" />
        </div>
        <div class="pm-form-group">
          <label for="pm-lastName">Nachname <span class="pm-required">*</span></label>
          <input type="text" id="pm-lastName" autocomplete="family-name" />
        </div>
        <div class="pm-form-group">
          <label for="pm-email">E-Mail-Adresse <span class="pm-required">*</span></label>
          <input type="email" id="pm-email" autocomplete="email" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pm-step" data-step="4">
        <h3>Adresse</h3>
        <div class="pm-form-group">
          <label for="pm-addressLine">Strasse und Hausnummer <span class="pm-required">*</span></label>
          <input type="text" id="pm-addressLine" autocomplete="street-address" />
        </div>
        <div class="pm-form-group pm-form-row">
          <div>
            <label for="pm-postalCode">PLZ <span class="pm-required">*</span></label>
            <input type="text" id="pm-postalCode" autocomplete="postal-code" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="pm-city">Ort <span class="pm-required">*</span></label>
            <input type="text" id="pm-city" autocomplete="address-level2" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pm-step" data-step="5">
        <h3>Einstellungen & Einwilligung</h3>
        <div class="pm-form-group">
          <label class="pm-checkbox-label">
            <input type="checkbox" id="pm-showName" />
            Meinen Namen auf dem Bodenplan anzeigen
          </label>
        </div>
        <div id="pm-displayName-wrap" class="pm-form-group pm-hidden">
          <label for="pm-displayName">Anzeigename <span class="pm-hint">(leer = Vor- und Nachname)</span></label>
          <input type="text" id="pm-displayName" placeholder="z.B. Familie Müller" />
        </div>
        <div class="pm-consent-block">
          <label class="pm-checkbox-label">
            <input type="checkbox" id="pm-consent" />
            Ich stimme zu, dass meine Daten zur Abwicklung der Passivmitgliedschaft gespeichert und verwendet werden. Die Daten werden nicht an Dritte weitergegeben.
          </label>
        </div>
        <div class="pm-turnstile-wrap">
          <div class="cf-turnstile" data-sitekey="@turnstileSiteKey" data-theme="light"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pm-step" data-step="6">
        <h3>Zusammenfassung</h3>
        <div class="pm-summary">
          <div class="pm-summary__row"><span class="pm-summary__label">Feld</span><span class="pm-summary__value" id="pm-sum-field">–</span></div>
          <div class="pm-summary__row"><span class="pm-summary__label">Stufe</span><span class="pm-summary__value" id="pm-sum-level">–</span></div>
          <div class="pm-summary__row"><span class="pm-summary__label">Name</span><span class="pm-summary__value" id="pm-sum-name">–</span></div>
          <div class="pm-summary__row"><span class="pm-summary__label">E-Mail</span><span class="pm-summary__value" id="pm-sum-email">–</span></div>
          <div class="pm-summary__row"><span class="pm-summary__label">Adresse</span><span class="pm-summary__value" id="pm-sum-address">–</span></div>
          <div class="pm-summary__row"><span class="pm-summary__label">Anzeige</span><span class="pm-summary__value" id="pm-sum-display">–</span></div>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#888;margin-top:1rem;">Mit «Jetzt anmelden» sendest du deine Anmeldung ab. Du erhältst eine Bestätigungs-E-Mail.</p>
        <div id="pm-step-error" class="pm-message pm-message--error pm-message--hidden" style="margin-top:0.75rem;max-width:100%;"></div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="pm-wizard__footer">
      <button class="pm-btn-back" type="button">Zurück</button>
      <button class="pm-btn-next" type="button">Weiter</button>
      <button id="pm-btn-submit" type="button" style="display:none">Jetzt anmelden</button>
    </div>

  </div>
</div> *@
